title: Burak Cankurtaran
author: Burak Cankurtaran
content: Today, I wanted to share with you a project that I have been following for a long time, Goldexplus. Goldexplus, a cold/hot wallet company, also offers a financial service to its users through various activities such as staking, farm, ico, ifo and airdrops in the platform. Finally, the campaign they announced is the 100% Busd campaign that will take place between 28 August and 15 September. announced. Those who are curious can find the details by searching @goldexplus on Twitter.
